sensing, intuiting.

00:19:15.620 --> 00:19:17.990 align:middle line:90%
These are the four functions.

00:19:17.990 --> 00:19:22.460 align:middle line:84%
And Jung often
noticed that people

00:19:22.460 --> 00:19:27.710 align:middle line:84%
seem to be developed more
or less with two of the four

00:19:27.710 --> 00:19:30.710 align:middle line:90%
strong and two of the four weak.

00:19:30.710 --> 00:19:33.730 align:middle line:84%
For example, it's
been suggested,

00:19:33.730 --> 00:19:35.960 align:middle line:84%
although it's not
true today, but it

00:19:35.960 --> 00:19:41.750 align:middle line:84%
