00:37:51.330 --> 00:37:54.900 align:middle line:84%
Put the mirror in, and it
has to go along both paths.

00:37:54.900 --> 00:37:56.520 align:middle line:84%
Take the mirror
out, it had to go

00:37:56.520 --> 00:37:58.440 align:middle line:90%
along one path and the other.

00:37:58.440 --> 00:38:01.790 align:middle line:84%
So we at the moment have
decided what the past

