00:55:50.350 --> 00:55:52.150 align:middle line:90%
Why do you do what you do, Fred?

00:55:52.150 --> 00:55:53.290 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGH]

00:55:53.290 --> 00:55:56.050 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: Well, my biggest
why isn't anything about me.

