something rather than nothing?

00:55:59.530 --> 00:56:02.420 align:middle line:90%
Why is there anything at all?

00:56:02.420 --> 00:56:05.950 align:middle line:84%
And why is there
an I-ness which is

00:56:05.950 --> 00:56:08.320 align:middle line:84%
capable of even asking
such a question as,

00:56:08.320 --> 00:56:10.480 align:middle line:84%
why is there something
rather than nothing?

00:56:10.480 --> 00:56:12.260 align:middle line:90%
Where does that all come from?

00:56:12.260 --> 00:56:14.530 align:middle line:84%
And to me, that's
the big mystery.

00:56:14.530 --> 00:56:16.940 align:middle line:84%
That's the mystery
