00:56:29.380 --> 00:56:33.290 align:middle line:84%
into the nature of what might
be called, quote, unquote,

00:56:33.290 --> 00:56:34.090 align:middle line:90%
"reality."

00:56:34.090 --> 00:56:35.030 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

00:56:35.030 --> 00:56:36.530 align:middle line:90%
What is reality, anyway?

00:56:36.530 --> 00:56:37.330 align:middle line:90%
OK.

