00:57:10.990 --> 00:57:14.410 align:middle line:84%
It's the observer
that has to change.

00:57:14.410 --> 00:57:16.215 align:middle line:84%
By changing the
observer, you create

00:57:16.215 --> 00:57:17.385 align:middle line:90%
and you change the reality.

00:57:17.385 --> 00:57:18.760 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And you
change your past,

00:57:18.760 --> 00:57:21.010 align:middle line:84%
and you change your future,
and you change everything.

00:57:21.010 --> 00:57:22.750 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: Yeah.

