Let's say you have a
significant other in your life,

00:57:27.550 --> 00:57:31.180 align:middle line:84%
and that significant other
could be another person who

00:57:31.180 --> 00:57:34.310 align:middle line:84%
is your same age, a younger
person, an older person,

00:57:34.310 --> 00:57:35.110 align:middle line:90%
whatever.

00:57:35.110 --> 00:57:37.970 align:middle line:84%
How do you bring your
I-ness to that person?

00:57:37.970 --> 00:57:41.830 align:middle line:84%
How do you make that
observation of that person?

00:57:41.830 --> 00:57:45.520 align:middle line:84%
How you do think when
