If you change how you
think about that person,

00:57:50.770 --> 00:57:55.440 align:middle line:84%
if you change who is thinking
about this other person,

00:57:55.440 --> 00:57:58.990 align:middle line:84%
if you just ask yourself
the question, who am I,

