or who is thinking
about this other person,

00:58:01.900 --> 00:58:06.400 align:middle line:84%
just asking that question to
yourself will change the way

00:58:06.400 --> 00:58:08.300 align:middle line:84%
you make the observation
of the other person.

00:58:08.300 --> 00:58:09.100 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

00:58:09.100 --> 00:58:11.770 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: And what'll
happen is the other person

00:58:11.770 --> 00:58:14.390 align:middle line:84%
