something different.

00:58:14.390 --> 00:58:18.630 align:middle line:84%
Just you-- you don't
have to even say a word.

00:58:18.630 --> 00:58:21.310 align:middle line:84%
You just in your
mind say to yourself,

00:58:21.310 --> 00:58:24.900 align:middle line:84%
who's asking about this
other person opposite me?

00:58:24.900 --> 00:58:25.970 align:middle line:90%
Who am I?

00:58:25.970 --> 00:58:26.770 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:58:26.770 --> 00:58:27.770 align:middle line:90%
A great example of that.

00:58:27.770 --> 00:58:31.900 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: If you don't
answer the question--

00:58:31.900 --> 00:58:32.800 align:middle line:90%
opposite.

00:58:32.800 --> 00:58:34.360 align:middle line:90%
You answer the question.

00:58:34.360 --> 00:58:39.410 align:middle line:84%
I am this other person's wife,
husband, father, mother, son,

00:58:39.410 --> 00:58:42.550 align:middle line:90%
daughter, enemy, friend.

00:58:42.550 --> 00:58:45.010 align:middle line:84%
Once you answer the
question in your mind,

00:58:45.010 --> 00:58:47.980 align:middle line:84%
you automatically
put on interaction

00:58:47.980 --> 00:58:53.680 align:middle line:84%
with that person in which that
person is going to psychically,

00:58:53.680 --> 00:59:00.730 align:middle line:84%
intuitively, in some way pick up
and will behave in relationship

00:59:00.730 --> 00:59:03.410 align:middle line:90%
with your way of observing.

00:59:03.410 --> 00:59:04.210 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:59:04.210 --> 00:59:06.310 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: And that is
what you need to do.

00:59:06.310 --> 00:59:10.180 align:middle line:84%
So what quantum physics tells
us, change the observer.

00:59:10.180 --> 00:59:12.010 align:middle line:90%
