Well, Mom, what are you doing?

00:59:57.730 --> 00:59:59.170 align:middle line:90%
What are you talk--

00:59:59.170 --> 01:00:00.540 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That's presence.

01:00:00.540 --> 01:00:01.660 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: Be present.

01:00:01.660 --> 01:00:02.840 align:middle line:90%
Let her do it.

01:00:02.840 --> 01:00:04.760 align:middle line:90%
But just stay with--

01:00:04.760 --> 01:00:05.560 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

