News comes in, it goes out.

01:00:32.010 --> 01:00:34.023 align:middle line:90%
It's like watching a TV drama.

01:00:34.023 --> 01:00:35.190 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yeah, it is a drama.

01:00:35.190 --> 01:00:37.440 align:middle line:90%
