01:00:37.440 --> 01:00:44.370 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: Observe without labeling
what or who you think you are.

01:00:44.370 --> 01:00:49.560 align:middle line:84%
Don't fixate on a
particular point of view.

01:00:49.560 --> 01:00:52.250 align:middle line:90%
